    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve factors meet or exceed required gradation levels. One factor (Test conditions) achieves Gradation 2 against a required Gradation 3, consistent with the single-configuration nature of ASTM F1717 and accepted regulatory practice for this device class. All three QoIs satisfy the pre-established quantitative acceptance bounds (E/uval < 1.96; relative difference < 10%). The FEA modeling framework is accepted as credible for the stated COU.",
